nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: When the number of job runs is greater than the default value for the MaxResults parameter, or if you explicitly specify a value for MaxResults that is less than the number of job runs, the response includes a pagination token named NextToken. You can specify this NextToken value in a subsequent call to ListJobRuns to list the next set of job runs.
